  • java.lang.Object
    • com.archql.labs.householddevices.Device
  • Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class Device
extends java.lang.Object
    class that holds general information of an abstract device property name refers to a product name property price refers to its cost property manufacturerName refers to a company name that produced the item property article refers to a unique code assigned to the item by manufacturer property isOnStall reflects if object is currently can be bought property price refers to its type
